Interface PBKDF2Formatter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PBKDF2HexFormatter

    public interface PBKDF2Formatter
    Copied from Matthias Gartner's PKCS#5 implementation - see http://rtner.de/software/PBKDF2.html
